theorem P3_inter {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hA : Topology.P3 A) (hB : Topology.P3 B) :
    Topology.P3 (A ∩ B) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3] at hA hB ⊢
  intro x hxAB
  rcases hxAB with ⟨hxA, hxB⟩
  have hxIntA : x ∈ interior (closure A) := hA hxA
  have hxIntB : x ∈ interior (closure B) := hB hxB
  have hIn : x ∈ interior (closure A) ∩ interior (closure B) :=
    ⟨hxIntA, hxIntB⟩
  have hsubset := interior_closure_inter_subset (A := A) (B := B)
  exact hsubset hIn

theorem interior_closure_empty {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    interior (closure (∅ : Set X)) = (∅ : Set X) := by
  simpa [closure_empty] using interior_empty
